cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is about image set classification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method uses Deep Extreme Learning Machines (DELM), which is a type of deep learning algorithm (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the non-linear structure of image sets, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the experiments involve datasets from video analysis (cs.MM) and image retrieval (cs.IR) domains.
